laazotea.indi.driver

Class INDISwitchOneOfManyProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • laazotea.indi.driver.INDIProperty
      • laazotea.indi.driver.INDISwitchProperty
        • laazotea.indi.driver.INDISwitchOneOfManyProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class INDISwitchOneOfManyProperty
extends INDISwitchProperty
    A class representing a INDI One Of Many Switch Property. It simplifies dealing with Switch elements and so on.
    Version:
    1.34, November 8, 2013
    Author:
    S. Alonso (Zerjillo) [zerjioi at ugr.es]
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
